## 🎯 Overview

This repository contains a comprehensive Claude Code configuration designed for full-stack development with intelligent multi-agent orchestration. It includes automated task analysis, smart model selection, and integration with Context7 for real-time documentation access.

### Key Capabilities

- **🧠 Intelligent Agent Orchestration**: 100+ specialized agents for every development need
- **📚 Context7 MCP Integration**: Real-time documentation for any library
- **🔄 Adaptive Model Selection**: Automatic selection between Haiku, Sonnet, and Opus
- **📊 Learning System**: Continuous improvement from usage patterns
- **🚀 Modern Stack Support**: Laravel, React, Next.js, TypeScript, Docker, and more

